messages.message:
Hi Team, We are have got new ticket for same issue.
Post weekly release when they ran the flow today, they are getting Incorrect API Key `"record=383124.tif.ibmsg column=__validate_all_field_prompt Exception Incorrect API key provided: sk-Miro9***************************************40ls. You can find your API key at https://platform.openai.com/account/api-keys. NoneType: None"` #6252 (https://instabase.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/6252). Could you please look into this.
CC : @chatur
I think this is because the key was updated manually, then the weekly release overwrote it
@MK I updated the openai key for this environment to the correct key.  I did it via a secret patch this time so it won't get overwritten again on the next deployment.
